8️⃣ Optional: Custom Validation Annotation

Example: Prevent self-transfer.

NoSelfTransfer.java
@Target(ElementType.TYPE)
@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)
@Constraint(validatedBy = NoSelfTransferValidator.class)
public @interface NoSelfTransfer {

    String message() default "Cannot transfer to same account";

    Class<?>[] groups() default {};

    Class<? extends Payload>[] payload() default {};
}

NoSelfTransferValidator.java
public class NoSelfTransferValidator
        implements ConstraintValidator<NoSelfTransfer, TransferRequest> {

    @Override
    public boolean isValid(TransferRequest request,
                           ConstraintValidatorContext context) {

        return !request.fromAccount()
                .equals(request.toAccount());
    }
}


Add annotation to record:

@NoSelfTransfer
public record TransferRequest(...)

